31#define __GMP_FORCE_mpz_neg 1
32
33#include "gmp.h"
34#include "gmp-impl.h"
35
36void
37mpz_neg (mpz_ptr w, mpz_srcptr u)
38{
39 mp_ptr wp;
40 mp_srcptr up;
41 mp_size_t usize, size;
42
43 usize = SIZ (u);
44
45 if (u != w)
46 {
47 size = ABS (usize);
48
49 wp = MPZ_NEWALLOC (w, size);
50
51 up = PTR (u);
52
53 MPN_COPY (wp, up, size);
54 }
55
56 SIZ (w) = -usize;
57}
